<br>
<p>Click on <b>Choose file</b>, Select the picture that will appear in the news. <br>Write the Title of the News on
  the
  <b>"Title of
    News column".</b><br>The <b>"PARAGRAPH column"</b> should contain the Body of the News<br>Then click on <b>"Upload
    News"</b> to upload the News to the Website.</p>
<br>
<div class="container-fluid">
  <div class="row">
    <div class="col-12 col-md-8 col-lg-6" id="kilo">
      <form action="" method="POST" enctype="multipart/form-data">
        <div class="custom-file">
          <input type="file" class="custom-file-input" name="image" required>
          <label for="image" class="custom-file-label"><b>UPLOAD PHOTO:</b></label>
        </div>
        <div class="form-group">
          <br>
          <label for="heading" class="custom-control-label"><b>TITLE OF NEWS:</b></label>
          <input type="text" class="form-control" name="heading" placeholder="Title" required>
        </div>
        <div class="form-group">
          <label for="passage" class="custom-control-label"><b>PARAGRAPH 1:</b></label>
          <textarea type="text" class="form-control" name="passage" placeholder="Paragraph 1..." required></textarea>
        </div>
        <div class="form-group">
          <label for="passage1" class="custom-control-label"><b>PARAGRAPH 2:</b></label>
          <textarea type="text" class="form-control" name="passage1" placeholder="Paragraph 2..."></textarea>
        </div>
        <div class="form-group">
          <label for="passage2" class="custom-control-label"><b>PARAGRAPH 3:</b></label>
          <textarea type="text" class="form-control" name="passage2" placeholder="Paragraph 3..."></textarea>
        </div>
        <br><br>
        <button type="submit" class="btn btn-primary"><b><span class="spinner-border spinner-border-sm"></span> UPLOAD
            NEWS</b></button>
      </form>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>
